CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 20, 2004

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1990-1780. State ex rel. Internatl. Union of Operating Engineers v. Cleveland.

Cuyahoga App. No. 57729. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellants’ motion for leave to respond to appellee’s reply brief,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for leave be, and hereby is, denied.
